## Adding Extensions to Visual Studio Code
1. Click on the Extensions icon in the Activity Bar.
2. Search for an extension in the Marketplace (e.g., Python, Prettier, etc.).
3. Click Install next to the extension you want.
4. Search for other Popular Extensions: Prettier: Code formatter
Python: Support for Python language features
